Package: occstanhm
Title: Multispecies occupancy models with Stan
Version: 2.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Richard", "Erickson", , "rerickson@usgs.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4649-482X")),
      person("Charlie", "Labuzzetta", , "clabuzzetta@usgs.gov", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6027-0120"))
      )
Description: occstanhm fits occupancy models (occ) using the Stan language
             (stan). These models are hierarchical both statistically and
             ecologically (hm). The package uses `cmdstanr` to run both within
             and among chain parallelization.
